Mozkey design reference
-----------------------

Project: https://github.com/koyasi777/mozkey

The delayed live-conversion debounce in Grimodex IME was independently
implemented with reference to Mozkey, an unofficial Mozc fork. Standard
Grimodex IME builds include no source code, model files, or dictionary data
from that project.

